next_seeds.title: Security Audit and Compliance Checks
next_seeds.rationale: Given the historical low coverage of security-related assessments, this iteration focuses on identifying security vulnerabilities using static analysis tools and penetration testing to improve overall robustness.

next_seeds.title: Enhancing Test Coverage with Mutation Testing
next_seeds.rationale: Building upon the previous work in test coverage, we'll introduce mutation testing to assess the quality of unit tests and ensure a more thorough evaluation of codebase resilience against bugs.

next_seeds.title: Architectural Design Review for Maintenance
next_seeds.rationale: With minimal architectural reviews so far, this seed idea aims to revisit system design principles focusing on scalability, maintainability, and long-term flexibility, ensuring we're not just focusing on immediate needs or short-term benefits.
